cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO 

This paper is about building detection using convolutional neural networks and a new benchmark dataset for roof segmentation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning methods for performance evaluation, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the dataset is related to remote sensing, which could place it in cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.RO (Robotics).
